hopobject.body: International directory enquiries permethrin 0 5 Up at State Parliament there was plenty of time for NSW Premier Barry O'Farrell to follow his progress and plot an intervention. In Sydney, it became one of the defining images of the campaign - O'Farrell striding towards Rudd, Rudd attempting to deflect him with a handshake, then turning away in obvious discomfort as O'Farrell berates him. Few could work out how Rudd's team had left him open to such an obvious risk of ambush.
